Key to the species of 
<taxonomicName box="[412,673,1592,1618]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Hoplitis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Formicapis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[412,508,1592,1618]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="111">Hoplitis</emphasis>
